Start app:
flask --app app run --debug

Create new student:
curl -X POST -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"name": "Anton"}' http://127.0.0.1:5000/students
curl -X POST -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{}' http://127.0.0.1:5000/students

Update student name by id:
curl -X PUT -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"name": "Updated Anton"}' http://127.0.0.1:5000/students/1
curl -X PUT -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"surname": "Updated Anton"}' http://127.0.0.1:5000/students/1

Get students list:
curl http://127.0.0.1:5000/students

Get student name by id:
curl http://localhost:5000/students/1
curl http://localhost:5000/students/0

Delete user by id:
curl -X DELETE http://localhost:5000/students/1
curl -X DELETE http://localhost:5000/students/0

